            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1598262786350-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Thai-style green king prawn curry</strong> over the<strong> lemongrass rice</strong></p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!), <strong>coriander leaves</strong> and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
